The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Rahim to Bangla rescue
                                                                                                                                                                                                     Rahim to Bangla rescue
                      
	Centurion: Mushfiqur Rahim rescued Bangladesh on the first day of the second and final Test against South Africa on Wednesday.         
	Rahim hit 65 in 86 balls and dominated a last-wicket stand of 56.           (REUTERS)                                                                                                                      
